       </p>
     </div>
     <div class="filter">
       <div>
         <i class="fa-solid fa-mountain-sun"></i>
       </div>
       <p>
         Mountains
       </p>
     </div>
     <div class="filter">
       <div>
         <i class="fa-solid fa-umbrella-beach"></i>
       </div>
       <p>
         Beach
       </p>
     </div>
     <div class="filter">
       <div>
         <i class="fa-brands fa-fort-awesome"></i>
       </div>
       <p>
        Historical
       </p>
     </div>
     <div class="filter">
       <div>
